          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
      <div class="team-cta-wrapper">
        <p class="team-tagline">
          Your official documents are handled by dedicated specialists and reviewed before delivery.
        </p>
        <a href="https://wa.me/971508620217" class="team-cta">
          <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> Send Documents on WhatsApp
